      <section class="implementation-process">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Our Comprehensive Implementation Process</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="implementation-step">
                        <h4>1. Initial Consultation</h4>
                        <p>Detailed assessment of your institution's unique requirements and existing infrastructure.</p>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled">
                            <li>Needs analysis</li>
                            <li>Current system evaluation</li>
                            <li>Custom solution design</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="implementation-step">
                        <h4>2. Tailored Configuration</h4>
                        <p>Custom setup and configuration of the ERP system to match your specific operational workflows.</p>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled">
                            <li>Module customization</li>
                            <li>Data migration strategy</li>
                            <li>Integration planning</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
